Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 992, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 373 - 1036, 428)"},{"index":1,"text":"APP真我: 都说双手是女人的第二张脸~ [图片] 殊不知，你的jio也是影响直观印象的重要因素！ 想象一下： 夏日阳光正好，你和你的男朋友一起在沙滩上追逐踩水，结果一低头，稀疏的沙子中露出一双晒得黑白界限分明的黝黑脚丫子~ 尴尬吗？ [图片] 冬日温泉边水雾腾腾，你和你男朋友穿着泳衣准备来个全身SPA的时候，一入水两只指甲老长、都是皱巴巴死皮和黄色厚茧的脚丫子被瞬间放大~ 尴尬吗？ [图片] 约会的时候，你男朋友为了表现自己暖男的形象，想亲手给你洗个ji…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_desc","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 722, 156)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 450 - 766, 606)"},{"index":2,"text":"等 303 人赞同","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/follow_user_action_text","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 229, 48)","boundsInScreen":"(162, 648 - 391, 696)"}]},{"index":2,"class":"android.view.ViewGroup","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 413)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 747 - 1080, 1160)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"有没有能让人变漂亮的好习惯？","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_title","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 992, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 786 - 1036, 841)"},{"index":1,"text":"APP真我: 小编一直觉得，无论是穿搭配饰、化妆，还是气质体态的培养，都属于锦上添花的作用。 而真正能够改变外貌形象的，是皮肤。 [图片] 毕竟一个人的第一印象，看到的都是面部。 而有一个好皮肤，不仅会给五官大大加分，还能帮助在妆面的塑造上更加自然。 但是皮肤管理并不是一蹴而就的事情，需要每天坚持保养，在一些护肤的细节上多多注意、多下功夫，才能维持一个良好的皮肤状态。 [图片] 皮肤状态，会随着年龄和环境不断变化，就算是一直自诩皮肤…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_desc","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 722, 156)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 863 - 766, 1019)"},{"index":2,"text":"等 155 人赞同","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/follow_user_action_text","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 223, 48)","boundsInScreen":"(200, 1061 - 423, 1109)"}]},{"index":3,"class":"android.view.ViewGroup","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 413)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 1160 - 1080, 1573)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"熬夜的危害是什么？","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_title","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 992, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1199 - 1036, 1254)"},{"index":1,"text":"APP真我: 百分百会变丑！ [图片] 英国的研究人员做过一次关于“ 睡眠时间”的实验研究。其中一位参与者叫做Sarah Chal mers ，已经46岁了。其实这个时候她的面部肌肤，已经随年龄出现的了一定的衰老，可是在“6小时”和“8小时”的睡眠时间里，我们还是可以从她脸上看到明显变化。 [图片] 左边是睡眠8小时，右边是睡眠6小时，可以明显看到相较于前者，后者出现了 面部浮肿 、没有血色、局部暗沉粗糙，双眼无声眼袋皱纹明显的等多个问题。除了这种实践，国外…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_desc","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 722, 156)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1276 - 766, 1432)"},{"index":2,"text":"等 601 人赞同","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/follow_user_action_text","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 224, 48)","boundsInScreen":"(200, 1474 - 424, 1522)"}]},{"index":4,"class":"android.view.ViewGroup","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 413)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 1573 - 1080, 1986)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"护发素的的正确使用方法是什么？","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_title","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 992, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1612 - 1036, 1667)"},{"index":1,"text":"APP真我: 大家对于护发素的了解，一般来自于洗发水配套销售。 hahaha！ 有多少人在买洗发水的时候，深深的感叹过： 就不能给我两瓶洗发水吗？ [图片] 因为一般情况下，洗发水用完了，护发素还剩大半瓶。但说真的，配套护发素其实也是为我们的头发护理考虑呢~ 洗发水能够具有很好地清洁效果，是因为里面的碱性成分。 但是这种成分的存在会让“发丝膨胀、毛鳞片张开”。 [图片] 对于已经有些受损、干燥的发质来说，只使用洗发水产品的话头发毛鳞片是无法闭…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/everyone_watching_desc","class":"android.widg